Well i had a few requests to upload my source when i uploaded my client, so here it is.
THERE ARE NO TROJANS !

Source download: http://uppit.com/7QU7NI

A few picutures ( sorry for 1 big one my MS paint was messin up) :
[IMG]http://i40.tinypic.com/14aezxt.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i40.tinypic.com/jhvkb5.jpg[/img]

Feel free to rep.
